<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yup, this is a Kunark item.<BR>
<BR>
Its dropped in the Lake of Ill Omen by Sarnak recruits (up to lvl 30) and legionnaires (Upto lvl 33)<BR>
<BR>
Its a very rare drop, common being hand woven armour (kinda like mesh with save buffs) and a sarnak embroidered tabard.</font></td></tr></table>
