<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>a good way to find these is to invis/camou/gather shadows yourself and walk around the fort.  If a recruit or legionnare attacks you WHILE you are invis, chances are that it has the bracer.</font></td></tr></table>
