<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Aeriana Windwalker</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-12 11:23:33</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I think the price set on this is a little high.  Yes, it is a rare drop, but the stats aren't that great.  What caster is going to remove their + WIS or INT bracer to replace it with a little AC and a see invis effect they could just cast if they wanted.  Melee classes could use it under certain circumstances, but chances are they'll take a higher AC item with some saves over this any day.  I looted this off a random Sarnak Lego just outside the castle entrance.  I ended up selling it to a guildmate at a good price (60pp more or less).  The only real use for this would be either in a duel vs an invis PC or I hear that some dungeons have invis MOBs.  You would probably just use it to spot a mob and quickly switch to your regular bracer.<BR>
<BR>
Just my 2cp</font></td></tr></table>
