<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hehe, sorry, I hit ENTER instead of TAB,<BR>
OK I do see your point, but are you going to remove your Serpentine Bracer or Bracer of Scavenging for this?  It's a constant effect, not the "right-click-to-use" type.  This means a potential DEX/AGI or whatever loss for the duration of the fight.  I really suspected this to be of the most use to melee types as you say, but not really THAT much use overall considering for less money than this site seems to want you can better round yourself out.<BR>
Like I said, this is just my opinion, I'm a caster and I can tell you it's pretty useless to me other than it makes a druid have plate arms which my Amethyst Bracer does anyway.<BR>
The AC is pretty good for a bracer dropped by a MOB easily killed by a group of mid-twenties, but the effect is not spectacular.</font></td></tr></table>
