<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I would like to clear up a few things....<BR>
<BR>
First of all this is a Random/Rare drop off of Sarnak Legionairres in Lake of Ill Omen.(not recruits). I have slain over 1000 of these mobs...(yes literally) and have only had it drop once.<BR>
<BR>
Secondly, this item *is* invaluable to non-casters, because of the unlimited effect... hence it's rarity.<BR>
<BR>
It is amusing that someone would say that they would rather have a serp over this.. as serps go for about 50p on my server ... and I was offered 2k and more on several occasions for this item.<BR>
<BR>
Have fun with your serps!<BR>
